<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I think it is quite good. We are all different, so I feel the &apos;cardboard cutouts&apos; opinion could be said of any characters in any book. I think she did<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I think it is quite good. We are all different, so I feel the 'cardboard cutouts' opinion could be said of any characters in any book. I think she did a good job of showing us without really understanding us<br /><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
