<span id="freeTextContainer15620781726395554378">5.0 stars. This is an incredible novel and one that I highly recommend to anyone one liked <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18373.Flowers_for_Algernon' title='Flowers for Algernon by Daniel Keyes' rel='nofollow noopener'>Flowers for Algernon</a>. Emotionally powerful science fiction at its best. Superb writing, excellent plot and an unforgetable main character. <br/><br/>Nominee: Arthur C. Clarke Award for Best Science Fiction Novel<br/>Nominee: Locus Award for Best Science Fiction Novel<br/>Winner: Nebula Award for Best Science Fiction Novel<br/><br/></span>
